But this sphere is always moving, never staying in one position.

30
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:49,000
Earth is orbiting a star, the Sun at the center of the solar system.

31
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:56,000
While we usually imagine this is pretty orderly, someone looking at us from the outside would see something pretty messy.

32
